Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限的时间将跳动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们悄声无息地燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界已经脱轨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸子西亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得变的好玩起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  好久没试过这样全力一战了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手干吧  我美丽的酒杯——玛丘莉·顿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}红莲的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「顶之座」——赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率领「扮装舞会」的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把悠二还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为容器已经结合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来她就是被这庞大的存在之力所充满的机关的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒她就能停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然除了阻止「顶之座」以外别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须尽快 这样下去城市会崩坏也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:04:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御崎市会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…得做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的思念正充满着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今以来不知结合了多少容器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把欲望全部吞噬也未曾得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要去赫卡特那了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再陪我打一会是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（继续战斗）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真缠人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…燃料过多也挺麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  看来会永远打下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千变」啊 这难道不是你们的目的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要…我的赫卡特能满足就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳…变态的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是玩人偶的料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 一定能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对的 阪井同学和小紫一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不能靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把阪井悠二从那里放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把零时迷子分离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的都应该会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用我的记忆和思念来充满自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在追寻着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:07:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触摸到你的时候终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我追寻着的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是单纯的火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是单纯的火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阪井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所追寻的是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实存在着的…我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实…容器最初重合的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是空无一物的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如此得被填满着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是我的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用别人的回忆来填满自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的你并不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作为火炬的你不也被阪井悠二的回忆所充满着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 与夏娜相遇的我果然只是个单纯的火炬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时就一直在思考着 苦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来的那些都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以再明确地说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阪井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于你的自己究竟在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填满我的东西…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会被我的回忆填满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从一开始就始终空无一物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…有人拜托我要带你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人和…吉田一美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在担心我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  最想这么做的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从一开始就始终空无一物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不是说好不能中途退出的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（异常事态）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「顶之座」正在将吞噬了的存在之力释放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这量…真是恐怖的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此庞大的存在之力回流的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕已经没空等着自然恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多~~~么精彩的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉还是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是超越了世界所能承受界限的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在之力的饱和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是待会要确认的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有唯一的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天壤之劫火」阿拉斯拖鲁的显现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显现？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是让阿拉斯拖鲁出现在这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为红世魔人的我的显现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会消耗大量的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用现在饱和的庞大存在之力来显现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计城市崩坏也会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果我显现的话 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为容器的火焰之雾也会被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经便是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏是指…难道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…会死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是炎发灼眼的火焰之雾被赐予的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全明白了这些才和阿拉斯拖鲁订下契约的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不好的预感是也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（急速前进）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为夏娜救了悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次要作为火焰之雾来完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪井悠二 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没时间带你逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和夏娜一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份心情现在也没变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天破壤碎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜欢悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（天破壤碎）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO~~~难得的饱和状态啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要着手准备下一个实验了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被「天壤之劫火」吞没的话就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的容器容纳了我的全部存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然订契约的时候我已经感觉到大小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 以后随时都可以出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话 赌上生命的行为怎么能一直尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原来还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也总算活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你干吗看别处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是夏娜你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦啰嗦啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比鲁海尔米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是走狗屎运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有资格说别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微离开下就这副德行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在照看下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~别转了喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊两位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.39,0:22:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐说暂时待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道好还是不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能老实一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:23:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜 今天晚饭会准备好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二学期胜负会分晓也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.49,0:23:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 池
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.59,0:23:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天第二回合开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:23:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.46,0:24:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带悠二回来的时候还哭着道谢的说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.18,0:24:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说那是第一回合
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.55,0:24:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此加油吧 小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.37,0:24:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将来也会一成不变的前进
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.64,0:24:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到在世界脱轨之前
